{"tid":1967331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天台屋暗藏富戶】戶主唔鎖門，引竊賊，招損失","createTime":"2020-04-10T22:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T06:05:22.000Z","uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"935cf93c5285f7a73fe88a335a55529774c6a516","tid":1967331,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T22:29:51.000Z","msg":"1. 旺角通菜街29號，<span style=\"color: red;\">天台屋單位</span>一對母子從澳洲返港，<br />\n<br />\n2. 發現屋內遭賊人爆竊搜掠，點算後發現連同屋契、一批金飾及海味被盜。經點損失5萬現金、30萬元外幣，5萬元金飾及萬多元平板電腦。總值40萬元，<br />\n<br />\n3. 兒子存放在屋內數本支票簿失去，並懷疑曾遭人多次冒簽提款，於是報案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 現場消息指<span style=\"color: red;\">遇竊單位沒有上鎖</span>，兩母子2月中往澳洲旅遊探親，其間一直未有回港。<br />\n<br />\n5. 至本周四（9日），20多歲兒子接獲銀行短訊及來電通知，其支票戶口有異動，涉款約百萬元，雖然未有成功過數，但亦急忙買機票回港。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc967a187e65421b2943ae501bebceca82a0390d","tid":1967331,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T22:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b08cfb20ce2e7b32765ed7b1d0425743414c3e6","tid":1967331,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T23:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d9c9162804112197e1a87d46a4deb6d7da6d48","tid":1967331,"uid":68478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T23:30:31.000Z","msg":"想呃保險？"},{"pid":"afff9dd2d2573edf6efef9e070e752707ca954d6","tid":1967331,"uid":52638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T23:31:16.000Z","msg":"可能租天台屋個單位當倉庫咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b17ac10c36211b2a5b8840312434300c92fea6","tid":1967331,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afff9dd2d2573edf6efef9e070e752707